    <section>
      <h2>Your Gateway to Building Professional Relationships</h2>
      <p>
        Developing your network is a key component of career success. The UMSI Networking & Connections Resource Hub is designed to empower you with the tools, strategies, and guidance you need to initiate and grow meaningful professional connections — whether you’re hoping to connect with peers, UMSI alumni, faculty, industry professionals, or potential mentors.
      </p>
    </section>


    <section>
      <h2>Why Networking Matters</h2>


      <ul>
        <li><strong>Expand Your Opportunities:</strong> Many jobs and internships are found through connections, not just online postings.</li>
        <li><strong>Build Lasting Relationships:</strong> Connect with mentors, peers, alumni, and professionals who can support your journey.</li>
        <li><strong>Learn from Others:</strong> Gather insights, advice, and real-world knowledge to inform your academic and career decisions.</li>
        <li><strong>Gain Visibility:</strong> Raise your professional profile within UMSI and the broader information field.</li>
        <li><strong>Access UMSI Events & Platforms:</strong> Explore exclusive events and platforms, like UMSI Career Link, to connect with the UMSI community and employers.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
